text: It was with great sadness that I learned today of the passing of former Congressman Joe Knollenberg. Our state and nation are better off because of his service. We go forward honoring Joe’s legacy and offer our prayers and sympathies to his family during this difficult time.
While I was not aboard the train this morning, at this time please join me in praying for all who were injured and their families

This week in the @FinancialCmte, we're discussing 17 bills, including one I introduced: #HR2255- The HOME Act; which allows mortgage appraisal services to be donated by fee appraisers to an organization that is eligible to receive tax-deductible charitable contributions.
